Project: NoteFlow (Mobile Productivity App)
Stack: Expo, TypeScript, React Native Paper, Zustand, Shopify FlashList, Zod.

Rules:
1. Always use functional components and hooks.
2. Store logic must remain in 'store/notesStore.ts'.
3. For FlashList type errors (ts2322), use 'const List = FlashList as any'.
4. Ensure all new screens are added to 'app/(tabs)' or as modals in 'app/'.
5. Use Haptics for success/error feedback.